<HEADLINE> PLA to Hold High Banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 13 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese People's
Liberation Army (PLA) will hold higher the great banner of Deng
Xiaoping Theory, rally more closely around the Central Committee
of the Communist Party of China (CPC) and actively promote the
army's building and reform, thus providing strong and powerful
guarantee for the implementation of the cross-century goals, PLA
delegates said in the panel discussion today.
</P>
<P>
The participants in the panel discussion included Zhang Zhen,
Zhang Wannian and Chi Haotian.
</P>
<P>
The report delivered by Jiang Zemin incisively points out the
noble historical responsibilities upon the Party over the destiny
of the nation, said Zhang Zhen.
</P>
<P>
The report gives a systematic exposition on the historic status
and guiding role of Deng Xiaoping Theory, and clearly puts forward
the political program, grand blueprint and strategic plan for
leading the cause of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics into the coming century, Zhang said, adding that
it reflects the wish of the whole Party and the entire Chinese
nation, and is thus an epoch-making programmatic document of
Marxism-Leninism, he said.
</P>
<P>
That holding high the banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory serves as
the soul of the congress has shown an adamant political stand and
outstanding leadership in the third generation of the CPC
leadership with Jiang Zemin at the core, Zhang added.
</P>
<P>
For a Party of 50 million-strong membership, and for a country
of 1.2 billion people and 56 nationalities, the advance of such an
unprecedented cause of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics would be impossible without a strong leadership,
Zhang said.
</P>
<P>
All officers and men in the army should consciously
safeguard the authoritativeness of leadership of the Party
Central Committee with Jiang Zemin at the core, he said.
</P>
<P>
The whole army should, whenever and wherever, be dedicated
heart and soul to the CPC Central Committee, and be in agreement
with the CPC Central Committee ideologically, politically and in
action. The whole army will firmly subject itself to the command
of the Party Central Committee and Central Military Commission
with Jiang Zemin at the core, Zhang Zhen said.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
