<DOCNO> XIE19970914.0015 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-14 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> PLA to Hold High Great Banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Zhang Wannian said the current Party congress has for the first
time defined the scientific concept of Deng Xiaoping Theory and
has written it down on the banner of the Communist Party of China
(CPC).
</P>
<P>
He said it has clearly stated that Deng Xiaoping Theory is the
guiding thought of the CPC and the spiritual support of the
Chinese nation as well as the great banner and guidance for
guiding China's reforms and opening-up and modernization drive.
</P>
<P>
The PLA is the people's armed forces under the leadership of
the CPC, and therefore, should hold high the great banner of
Deng Xiaoping Theory, Zhang said.
</P>
<P>
He said it is the most important political entrust of Deng
Xiaoping in his lifetime to firmly support the Party Central
Committee with Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core.
</P>
<P>
Practice has proved that Jiang Zemin has been a loyal, reliable
and promising successor to the cause of building socialism with
Chinese characteristics initiated by Deng Xiaoping, he said. And
the CPC Central Committee with Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core is
a sophisticated leading collective which can handle various
complicated situations and it has been highly trusted and
respected by the whole Party, the whole army and people from
various nationalities.
</P>
<P>
Zhang called on PLA officers and men to rally more
closely around the Party Central Committee with Jiang Zemin at
the core and obey the instructions of the Party Central
Committee.
</P>
<P>
Zhang Wannian urged the PLA officers to promote army building
and its reform and attach great importance to quality building in
line with Deng Xiaoping Theory and a series of instructions by
Jiang Zemin to advance along the road of fewer but better troops
with Chinese characteristics and provide strong security guarantee
for realizing the trans-century goals.
</P>
</TEXT>
