<DOCNO> XIE19970914.0017 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-14 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> PLA To Hold High Banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Chi Haotian said that Jiang Zemin's report, centering around
speeding up the economic development, taking into consideration
the global military development trend and China's actual
conditions and military development, sets new demands on
cross-century national defense and army building.
</P>
<P>
This indicates that the Party Central Committe attaches great
importance to the army building and the improvement of the
strength of national defense, he said.
</P>
<P>
"So long as we hold high the great banner of Deng Xiaoping
Theory and take Deng Xiaping's military thinking as the guiding
principle, the objective of military modernization will surely be
achieved no matter what difficulties we may face," he said.
</P>
<P>
A fundamental political system of the Chinese army is to
persist in the principle of absolute leadership of the Party over
the army, he said.
</P>
<P>
To do this, he added, it is necessary to safeguard the
authority of the Party Central Committee with Jiang Zemin as the
core. This was the most important political behest of Deng
Xiaoping, he added.
</P>
<P>
"We must treasure the hard-won situation, support the Party
Central Committee and obey orders of the Party Central
Committee and the Central Military Commission," he said.
</P>
<P>
He urged the whole army to implement the tasks on army building
set by the 15th Party Congress, readjust the establishment of the
army units, intensify scientific research on national defense and
raise the level of weaponry while serving and being subordinated
to the national economic construction. 
</P>
</TEXT>
