<HEADLINE> GCC Welcomes Albright's Peace Efforts </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, September 14 (Xinhua) -- The Gulf Cooperation
Council (GCC) today welcomed efforts employed by the U.S.
Secretary of State Madeleine Albright to revive the Middle
East peace process.
