<HEADLINE> Li Ruihuan Emphasizes Need to Study Theory on Primary Stage of Socialism  (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 14 (Xinhua) -- Li Ruihuan said here today
that the theory on the primary stage of socialism is the
corner stone of Deng Xiaoping Theory.
</P>
<P>
The theory on the primary stage of socialism is the basis of
our Party in formulating policies, he said at a panel discussion
with delegates from the north China port city of Tianjin.
</P>
<P>
"Only when we understand the theory on the primary stage of
socialism, can we know clearly that why our Party pursues this
principle in this stage in stead of practising other policies and
principles, and conscientiously implement Party's basic line," he
said.
</P>
<P>
A full understanding on the theory of primary stage of
socialism will help us to distinguish the right from wrong,
maintain vigilance against the Right tendencies, but first against
the "Left" and take the "three favorables", namely favorable to
promoting the growth of the productive forces in a socialism
society, increasing the overall strength of the socialist state
and raising the people's living standards, as the basic criterion,
he said.
</P>
<P>
The significance of the theory on the primary stage of
socialism lies in a clear understanding about the protracted
nature and arduousness of the cause of socialism, he said.
</P>
<P>
"We admit that the productive forces at present in China is
relatively backward, which can't be compared with that in the
developed countries nor that even in some developing countries,"
he said.
</P>
<P>
It requires the efforts of several generations and even dosens
of generations to consolidate and develop socialist system.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
