medal, defeating Brazil 12-4, 12-6. In the bronze medal match,
Argentina beat Japan 12-3, 12-5.
</P>
<P>
The US women made it a clean sweep in the tournament by
defeating Australia 12-2, 12-5, with Canada taking home the bronze
with a three-game, one hour match against Japan 12-7, 10-12, 12-10.
</P>
<P>
